Yet on matters close to , er , home ...
`` The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">HUD</ENAMEX> budget has dropped by <ENAMEX TYPE="PERCENT">more than 70 %</ENAMEX> since <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1980</ENAMEX> , '' argues Mr. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Colton</ENAMEX> .
